This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image and video processing. The mention of different evaluation metrics and datasets suggests that it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the mention of real-time processing suggests that it may belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
